Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.88,0:00:09.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,认为发光体\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and believed that the illuminated stuff...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.34,0:00:12.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是构成我们宇宙的一切\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}was all that made up our universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.39,0:00:19.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,科学家现在认识到了并非闪闪发光的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Scientists now realize it's not what shines in the light...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.39,0:00:21.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而是隐藏在暗处的东西\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but what hides in the dark...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.31,0:00:24.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掌握着我们天空真正的秘密\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that holds the true secrets of our sky.
