Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.45,0:00:36.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是始作俑者\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}might be to blame.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.95,0:00:40.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一种黑暗的排斥能量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And there is a dark, repulsive energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.95,0:00:44.20,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正在创造宇宙的空间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that is creating space in the universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.25,0:00:47.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但又在将星系逐步逐步地拆散\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but driving the galaxies further and further apart...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.67,0:00:49.04,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直至悲惨的结局\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}to a dismal fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.09,0:00:54.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,暗物质和暗能量结合在一起\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Combined, dark matter and dark energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.26,0:00:58.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,占到了宇宙的96%\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}make up ninety-six percent of the universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.39,0:01:00.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,揭开它们的秘密\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and uncovering their secrets...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.35,0:01:03.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像是百步穿杨\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is like making the one-in-a-million shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.22,0:01:07.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一旦揭开 宇宙的最终结局\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lf uncovered, the ultimate fate of the universe...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.10,0:01:08.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就有可能被揭示\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}might be revealed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.56,0:01:15.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它会是在引力的猛烈撞击中垮塌燃烧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Will it crash and burn in a horrific collision...of gravitational forces...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.78,0:01:20.07,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是暗能量将宇宙撕得粉碎呢？\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}or will dark energy tear the universe apart?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.12,0:01:24.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,打赌 宇宙将葬身冰寒\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The betting is the universe will die in ice.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.16,0:01:27.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了解这两个量… 暗物质和暗能量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Understanding these two quantities, dark matter and dark energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.96,0:01:30.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其实是了解宇宙的根本\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is really fundamental to understanding the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.96,0:01:34.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是一次宇宙黑暗一面的旅行\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This is a trip to the dark side of the universe.
