Dialogue: 0,0:43:35.40,0:43:39.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2000年以来探索自然法则的最大成就\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ever since the Greeks asked the question..."What are things made of?"
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.61,0:43:44.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,目前 暗物质和暗能量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}For now, dark matter and dark energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.41,0:43:50.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是21世纪有待解决的最大的宇宙问题\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}continue to be the greatest cosmological questions...of the 21st century.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.71,0:43:51.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这当然令人沮丧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's certainly frustrating.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:51.75,0:43:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的意思是令人感到难为情 去了解\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Yes, l mean, it's humbling, too, to know that...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.00,0:43:57.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道吗 我们所有的物理知识\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}you know, all that we know about physics...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.50,0:43:59.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,局限于普通物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is restricted to normal matter...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.17,0:44:02.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是所有这些暗物质 暗能量\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and yet there's all this other dark matter and dark energy...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.26,0:44:04.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们真的了解甚少\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that we really understand very little about.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.97,0:44:12.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是揭开宇宙黑暗一面的新纪元的开始\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's the beginning of a new era and the mysteries...of the dark side of the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.19,0:44:14.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里是粒子天体物理学方面的大西部\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's the Wild West as far as particle astrophysics...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.02,0:44:16.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我们对这个领域的称谓\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}which is what we call this field.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.69,0:44:20.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这就是我们尚未完全了解的空间特性\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}lt's a property of space that we don't yet fully understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.00,0:44:27.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢观赏\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Thanks For Viewing
